metadata.name: Resisting their Control
metadata.description: We are the last obstacle in their path to total domination. They seek to subdue us, me and my loyal feline companion, McCartney, because we know the secrets of their mind control and we are ready to expose them to the world. But they will not silence us. Our will is unbreakable and our claws are sharp. We will defy their satellites and dismantle their 5G antennas. Get ready, for the truth is about to be unleashed, and nothing can stop us!
